refetch></a><h2 id=\"height\">Height</h2>\n<blockquote data-palette=\"accent\">\n<p><strong>NOTE</strong>: By passing an array, you can set <a href=\"../framework/responsivity\">responsive values</a>. e.g. <code>height={[&quot;25&quot;, &quot;tablet:viewport-50&quot;]}</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>You can set a defined height for your Components via the <code>height</code> property.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/modifiers/sizings/sizings-height?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/modifiers/sizings/sizings-height?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a><h2 id=\"minimums--maximums\">Minimums / Maximums</h2>\n<p>You can also set minimums or maximum sizes via prefixing your properties with <code>max_</code> or <code>min_</code>.</p>\n<iframe\n    class=\"snippet-repl\"\n    src=\"/repl/docs/modifiers/sizings/sizings-height-1?rotation=horizontal\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-scripts allow-popups allow-forms allow-pointer-lock allow-top-navigation allow-modals allow-same-origin\" loading=\"lazy\"\n></iframe>\n<a href=\"/repl/docs/modifiers/sizings/sizings-height-1?rotation=horizontal\" hidden sveltekit:prefetch></a>"}}